### Test all endpoints after HTTP method mapping fix

### Get all jobs (should work in browser now)
GET http://localhost:8082/api/jobs

### Create a job
POST http://localhost:8082/api/jobs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Java Developer Intern",
  "company": "TechCorp",
  "description": "Java development role working on Spring Boot backend",
  "stipend": "15000",
  "location": "Bangalore"
}

### Search for jobs
GET http://localhost:8082/api/jobs/search?keyword=java

### Update job (assuming ID 1)
PUT http://localhost:8082/api/jobs/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Senior Java Developer",
  "company": "Infosys",
  "location": "Bangalore",
  "description": "Updated job description"
}

### Delete job (assuming ID 1)
DELETE http://localhost:8082/api/jobs/1
